45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過用酒精濕紙巾抹機身同鏡，唔知係咪因為抹完有靜電所以部機成日痴晒塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時一拎出黎冇耐就勁多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人分享平時用咩工具同點清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪都不外乎lens pen果啲?</blockquote><br />\n酒精抹手柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塊膠皮溶咪痴塵囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有機溶劑都用黎抹膠製品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁塊膠溶左係咪冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁理論上啲溶劑都會揮發嘅，唔會無了期＂乸＂你部機的<br />\n不過以後都黐立立就梗加啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啲相機配件鋪賣買啲酒精其實係用黎抹啲咩咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n酒精你當係抹油抹指模<br />\n但抹得多前鏡多多少少會影響個coating<br />\n<br />\n溶左膠唔識只會越搞越衰<br />\n照用算啦，一係就換皮</blockquote><br />\n痴L線相機鋪搵鬼有賣酒精<br />\n個啲係日蝕水<br />\n你用左酒精抺鏡嘅話你枝鏡已經報左廢<br />\n前面coating會洗走左，枝鏡對炫光能力會收皮"},{"pid":"b6523d4ef8f23ae64d8c46f6e5e76e1020b0537c","tid":124841,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T19:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機身買條2蚊店洗碗布少少濕抹<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭早已入塵，少理，吹下佢算<br />\n<br />\n反而好好好耐唔時會除鏡頭手拎個膠環<br />\n除出來洗潔精洗走哂白色汗漬<br />\n一年一次左右啦</blockquote><br />\n<b